íŸ@26c72fdd28b14bd85c6e830a5d407f97b584a2d6ed8c412ebd87913527c7f23d⁄5Title: title: polars sample
Path: Flags
Content:
``--n-rows, -n {int}``
: Number of rows to be taken from dataframe.
``--fraction, -f {number}``
: Fraction of dataframe to be taken.
``--seed, -s {number}``
: Seed for the selection.
``--replace, -e``
: Sample with replace.
``--shuffle, -u``
: Shuffle sample.
